description: Professional Grade General Purpose Electrical Tape

MAT Electrical Tape is 9mm wide Plasticized PVC film with an aggressive rubber based adhesive in OSHA colors; rolls are individually cello-wrapped and labeled. It is a UL/CSA 1.5 in. listed core. Flame retardant and cold resistant.
